official_title: A bill to amend the Social Security Act to eliminate family planning services and supplies from the ceiling presently imposed on the total amount of Federal payments which may be made to Puerto Rico, the Virgin Islands, or Guam in any fiscal year under the medicaid program.

summary.text: Eliminates family planning services and supplies from the ceiling presently imposed on the total amount of Federal payments which may be made to Puerto Rico, the Virgin Islands, or Guam in any fiscal year under the medicaid program of the Social Security Act.
